(en) MFT completed its exploitation of the house; Vicinity grid: 12 SWG 6050 8870, believed to be occupied by Mattu Zimmie. Findings: 1 x computer, pictures and videos of current actions against the Army forces in their AO. 20 of 20 personnel associated with this cell have been captured — Mattu Zimmie is wanting to share further information of other operatives with U.S. Forces. Small arms and IED making materials were also found on the site. Personnel detained are being processed for further questioning. This splinter cell is deemed no longer to be a threat to current operations at this time.
